          "contents": "from neighborhood import Painter\nfrom custom import turn_right\n\nrylee = Painter()\n\nwhile rylee.can_move():\n  rylee.move()\n  # TODO - Modify this if statement to check if the Painter can move south\n  if rylee.can_move():\n    turn_right(rylee)\n    rylee.move()",
